constraint: The name shall only contain letters a-z, letters A-Z and space characters.
The name shall contain at least one space character.
The name shall not end with a space character.
The name shall not start with a space character.
function:
def this_function(s: str) -> bool:
    ''' 
    Check if the name does not start with a space character.
    
    Returns True if the name does not start with a space, 
    otherwise returns False.
    '''
    return not s.startswith(' ')
